name: The Penthouse -  majestic and panormic seascapes
description:
Elegantly designed by award-winning architect Stefan Antoni, each living area creates a space that allows for comfortable living with unrestricted, uncluttered
spaces that gracefully mimic tranquility.

This North facing penthouse apartment is perfectly complemented by private balconies that are carefully designed to optimize views of the ocean, mountain and iconic Robben Island.

The space
This penthouse apartment offers 5 Executive bedrooms with ensuite bathrooms, plus 2 full bathrooms / guest toilets and outdoor shower with sea view.

A large rooftop garden with full size heated pool and two sea facing patios and 1 dip pool. Informal and formal lounge and dining areas, playroom, poolroom, study, bar area.

Filled with an endless list of distinctive features which coupled with Stefan Antoni’s careful consideration to facilities and functionality provides the perfect penthouse apartment for an unrivaled experience.

neighborhood_overview: Trendy Mouille Point is known for posh fish restaurants and steakhouses with oceanfront patios, and for the Sea Point Promenade, which winds along the oceanfront past the red-striped Green Point Lighthouse. A playground with an ice rink and miniature railway attracts families at Blue Train Park, and nearby Green Point Park has trails, a hedge maze and the Cape Town Stadium sports and concert venue.

name: Retreat to a Luxury Villa in Prime Location
description:
Welcome to our stunning contemporary home in prime location of Camps Bay with breathtaking sea and mountain views, just minutes away from the beach and restaurants. Open the glass patio doors and experience a free-flowing paradise and incredible sunsets behind the infinity pool. With brand new, high-end designer furnishings, this immaculate home conveys luxury inside and out. Get ready to relax while we provide concierge and cleaning service, airport transfer and a generous welcome basket.

The space
This open plan villa is well positioned to maximize the views of the Atlantic ocean, Table Mountain and Lions Head from each room. Two separate indoor entertainment lounges with glass sliding doors lead to a magnificent outdoor tanning area with a full-size infinity pool, lounge chairs, tables and umbrellas. The perfect place to enjoy your afternoon, sipping on one of the Cape’s world-famous wines or evening barbecue with your friends or family.

Camps Bay is Cape Town’s most prestigious and fashionable area.
Ideally located between the azure of the Atlantic and Table Mountain, while close to Cape Town’s Central Business district. Camps Bay is the most sought after

Admire the breathtaking views, enjoy beautiful white-sand beaches and gourmet beach front restaurants.

name: Luxury & Ultra Modern Lifestyle SaltLife Camps Bay
description:
This ultra-modern luxury home in Camps Bay has a breath-taking panoramic view over the Atlantic Ocean allowing for spectacular sunsets in the evening. You can enjoy views of Lions Head & Table Mountain's Cable Car from the Jacuzzi.
This apartment is very spacious and has lots of day light and actually feels more like a free standing home than an apartment.
Perfectly located in a cosmopolitan seaside village, 2 min walk to iconic white beaches and vibey promenade with many restaurants and shops

The space
The villa has 4 beautiful and spacious king bedrooms with private bathrooms, TV and mood lighting. The living and dining area is stylish and elegant, and enjoys spectacular ocean views.
Guests can enjoy Alexa home automation and complimentary Wi-Fi access.
The Villa has an expansive entertainment area; 18-metre lap pool, Jacuzzi, outdoor dining and lounge area, pizza oven and gas barbecue facility; a perfect area to relax and enjoy sun-downers,
neighborhood_overview:
Camps Bay is located at the foot of the Twelve Apostles mountain range and adjacent to Table Mountain. The seaside village has it all, including stunning beaches like iconic Clifton beach, trendy bars and restaurants offering an array of diverse cuisines, great shopping, and a small beachfront market. It's a lovely, safe neighborhood, just a 15 minute drive to the city centre and 20 minutes from the V&A Waterfront.
This is an ideal base from which to explore wider horizons or enjoy a relaxed and peaceful beach holiday.

description:

Otherwise, step indoors to escape to one of the plush bedrooms, or open plan living area with floor-to-ceiling glass doors serving superlative views. This is one for the books. Look no further.

Go for hikes in the mountains and see the spectacular views from many different angles.  The beach area is called  "the strip" and is host to a variety of famous and excellent restaurants and bars with a buzz of fame and fortune. This truly is the playground of the rich.

name: The Steensway Villa - on the beach in Llandudno
description:
The Steensway is a warm and modern home that is situated on the front row of the beautiful Llandudno Beach, and has its own private path down to the beach.

The Villa offers guests a luxurious space to relax and recharge while discovering all that Llandudno and The Cape have to offer.

The space
This luxurious home is an absolute sanctuary, a place for the whole family to come together, to relax and recharge.

We have a private path to Llandudno beach and uninterrupted views of the ocean as far as the eye can see.

The sea facing balconies are perfect for sunrise yoga, laid back breakfasts and evening sundowners. Gather around the braai (BBQ) on the downstairs deck or have a dip in the private heated pool.

We have a wonderful downstairs entertainment area, with a state of the art sound system, large LED TVs, outdoor swing chairs, (our favourite for a sundowner!) a fully equipped kitchen and space for the kids to play! <
neighborhood_overview:
Llandudno is a beautiful and quiet beach residential area. The closest amenities can be found in Hout Bay (5 minutes drive), Camps Bay (10 minutes drive) and Constantia (15 minutes drive).

We are spoilt for choice in terms of coffee shops, exceptional restaurants and spas and we have the Camps Bay nightlife around the corner. The exquisite V&A Waterfront boasts incredible food, 5 star restaurants and the best shopping in Cape Town. Let us know if you require a table booked, or a spa treatment arranged, we are here to help!
host_location: Cape Town, Western Cape, South Africa
host_about: Cape Town born and bred, I’ve grown up loving and living all that it means to be a South African. Nature, horses, barefoot children, lots of dogs and cats, wild African storms and sticky, stary summer nights. I’m a yoga loving, nature junkie mom of two, business owner and founder of The Gift of The Horse.
